data.name: CreateDashboardStagingPriority35
ReadCaseCaseAssignment
data.value: select T1.NUMB, T1.STATUS, T1.STATUS_DATE, T1.CSE_OPEN_DATE, T1.NO_JURISDICTION_CD, T2.EFFECTIVE_DATE, T2.DISCONTINUE_DATE, T2.CREATED_TIMESTAMP, T2.SPD_ID, T2.OFF_ID, T2.OSP_CODE, T2.OSP_DATE from CKT_CASE T1 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_ASSIGN_CASE T2 with(readuncommitted) on T1.NO_JURISDICTION_CD = ' ' and T1.NUMB = T2.CAS_NO and T2.EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @effectiveDate and T2.DISCONTINUE_DATE >= @discontinueDate and T1.NUMB > @numb and ( T1.STATUS = 'C' and (T1.STATUS_DATE between cast(@discontinueDate as date) and cast(@effectiveDate as date)) or T1.STATUS_DATE > @effectiveDate and T1.STATUS = 'O' ) order by T1.NUMB, T2.EFFECTIVE_DATE desc

data.name: ReadCseOrganization
data.value: select ORGANZTN_ID, TYPE_CODE from CKT_CSE_ORGANIZATN with(readuncommitted) where TYPE_CODE = 'J' order by ORGANZTN_ID

data.name: ReadDashboardStagingPriority1
data.value: select REPORT_MONTH, REPORT_LEVEL, REPORT_LEVEL_ID, AS_OF_DATE, CASES_CLS_W_ORDER, CASES_CLS_WO_ORDER from CKT_DB_STAGE_PRI35 where REPORT_MONTH = @reportMonth and REPORT_LEVEL = 'JD'

data.name: ReadDashboardStagingPriority2
data.value: select REPORT_MONTH, REPORT_LEVEL, REPORT_LEVEL_ID, AS_OF_DATE, CASES_CLS_W_ORDER, CASES_CLS_WO_ORDER from CKT_DB_STAGE_PRI35 with(xlock) where REPORT_MONTH = @reportMonth and REPORT_LEVEL = @reportLevel and REPORT_LEVEL_ID = @reportLevelId

data.name: ReadInfrastructure
data.value: select SYSTEM_GENERATED_I, EVENT_ID, EVENT_TYPE, EVENT_DETAIL_NAME, CASE_NUMBER, CREATED_TIMESTAMP from CKT_INFRASTRUCTURE where CASE_NUMBER = @caseNumber and (EVENT_DETAIL_NAME in ('CASECLOSED', 'CASEWCLOSEDWOCAU')) and (CREATED_TIMESTAMP between cast(@timestamp1 as datetime2) and cast(@timestamp2 as datetime2))

data.name: UpdateDashboardStagingPriority35
data.value: update CKT_DB_STAGE_PRI35 set AS_OF_DATE = @asOfDate, CASES_CLS_W_ORDER = @casesClsWOrder, CASES_CLS_WO_ORDER = @casesClsWoOrder where REPORT_MONTH = @reportMonth and REPORT_LEVEL = @reportLevel and REPORT_LEVEL_ID = @reportLevelId
